File::TinyLock version 0.10
=======================

File::TinyLock provides a lock function for locking files.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

none

